</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eciypse>EcIypse</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myoswego.net/~mojoteq/pics/17anidot5c.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#333333>(2/5/03 3:59:54 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels2428.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Najena at level 27?</span><hr size=1> Iron Oxides still sell pretty well, and It really is worth spending some time in here if you want your foci (which you should) or ever plan on doing your epic. I personally would rather get some XP while I am trying to get pages than sitting there camping greenies. At level 26 I had all 4 foci, and they make a huge difference! <p>      <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Love is the answer; but while you're waiting for the answer, sex raises some pretty good questions.&quot; (Woody Allen) </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=moedrippins>Moe Drippins</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 21<br> <font color=#333333>(2/5/03 6:28:03 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels2428.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Foci?</span><hr size=1> Just started a mage; lvl 15 right now.  Are there any guides around about the focus items?  How to get them, when to start, etc? <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=moedrippins>Moe Drippins</A> at: 2/5/03 6:28:32 pm<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=eciypse>EcIypse</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.myoswego.net/~mojoteq/pics/17anidot5c.gif " BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 27<br> <font color=#333333>(2/5/03 6:50:58 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels2428.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Foci?</span><hr size=1> goto Allakhazams for the info, it is pretty basic. <p>      <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em>&quot;Love is the answer; but while you're waiting for the answer, sex raises some pretty good questions.&quot; (Woody Allen) </em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#989dca><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub102.ezboard.com/bthemagicianstower.showUserPublicProfile?gid=ailurya@themagicianstower>Ailurya</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Magician</span><br>  Posts: 41<br> <font color=#333333>(2/11/03 1:35:49 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlevels2428.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=166.topic&index=7>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Watch out for unexpected adds</span><hr size=1> Should be safe with a bit of care, but I just got killed in Najena at 35 by a mob of magicians, Rathyl, Moosh and Ekeros who all decided to join in when I attacked the first magician outside Rathyl's room. All but Rathyl (light blue) and Rathyl Incarnate (dark blue) were green, but even my MS1 self-DS-ed pet couldn't quite handle six or seven of them (plus pets) simultaneously when most were casters.<br>
<br>
